<p><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781683695059" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="259256" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/15-novels-you-need-to-read-this-fall/greatwork/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork.jpg" data-orig-size="800,447" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="greatwork" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork-300x168.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork.jpg" class="aligncenter wp-image-259256 size-full" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="447" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork.jpg 800w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork-300x168.jpg 300w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork-768x429.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork-60x34.jpg 60w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/greatwork-50x28.jpg 50w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></p>
<h2><strong>Sheldon Costa,<a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781683695059" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em> The Great Work</em></a><br />
